title: Provides for special license plates for the New York city auxiliary police
summary: Allows the commissioner of motor vehicles, upon request, to issue special license plates for members of the New York city auxiliary police; provides that such distinctive license plates shall bear the letters "NYCAP"; sets fees for the issuance of such license plates.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the vehicle and traffic law, in relation to special license plates for the New York city auxiliary police
